---
import Card from "../Card.astro";
---

<section id="next-section" class="py-20 px-8 pt-24 z-30 text-white relative">
	<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
		<h2 class="text-5xl font-bold mb-8">
			artful <span class="italic text-orange-500">systems</span>.
		</h2>
		<p class="text-xl max-w-xl mx-auto font-semibold">
			sudo.create crafts cinematic stories and the systems that keep them
			breathing. Strategy, tools, workflows — all built so your work
			repeats beautifully. Photos, video, and sound: assets that actually
			earn their place.
		</p>
	</div>
	<div class="mt-12 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mx-auto">
		<Card>
			<span class="badge badge-accent badge-lg"
				>cinematic storytelling</span
			>
			<p class="font-semibold text-xl max-w-md mt-4">
				Every frame matters. Every asset must pull its weight. We shoot
				with reuse in mind — media shot, tagged, and shaped to plug
				straight into your channels and your story.
			</p>
			<div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 mt-6 lg:h-[500px]">
				<figure class="rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
					<img
						class="w-full h-full object-cover"
						src="/images/tourpass.png"
					/>
				</figure>
				<figure class="rounded-xl overflow-hidden h-full">
					<img
						class="w-full h-full object-cover"
						src="/images/tourpass.png"
					/>
				</figure>
			</div>
		</Card>

		<Card>
			<span class="badge badge-secondary badge-lg">creative systems</span>
			<p class="font-semibold text-xl max-w-md mt-4">
				Creativity needs infrastructure. We build blueprints and content
				engines — templates, automations, and workflows that keep chaos
				out and craft in. We make your process repeatable. And yes, we
				make it fun. (You're welcome.)
			</p>
			<div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 mt-6 lg:h-[500px]">
				<figure class="rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
					<img
						class="h-full w-full object-cover"
						src="images/evolutionary-blades.png"
					/>
				</figure>
				<figure class="rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
					<img
						class="h-full w-full object-cover"
						src="images/evolutionary-blades.png"
					/>
				</figure>
			</div>
		</Card>
	</div>
</section>
